NK032(khi)009:1: // snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i man ngag gi khog chings bzhugs /
NK032(khi)009:2: rang sems sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)009:3: rdzogs pa chen po snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i
NK032(khi)009:4: khog chings bka' yi ngos 'dzin 'di la spyir grub
NK032(khi)009:5: mthas blos bsgyur ba la gnyis su 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)009:6: phyi pa mu stegs pa dang /
NK032(khi)009:7: nang pa sangs rgyas pa gnyis las /
NK032(khi)009:8: 'di ni nang pa sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK032(khi)009:9: nang ba la rgyu mtshan nyid dang /
NK032(khi)009:12: gsang sngags gsar rnying gnyis las /
NK032(khi)009:14: rnying mal theg pa rim pa dgu ru 'dod pa las /
NK032(khi)009:16: de yang bka' sa man+ta nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK032(khi)009:17: ma 'gags skye ba med pas a //
NK032(khi)009:18: ma bsgom dbyings su thim pas ti //
NK032(khi)009:20: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga la /
NK032(khi)009:21: bka' ma gter ma gnyis las /
NK032(khi)009:23: bka' ma la slob dpon bee ro tsa nas bstan pa'i brgyud pa dang po /
NK032(khi)009:27: spyir rdzogs pa chen po'i spyi rgyud /
NK032(khi)009:28: bka' sa man+ta nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK032(khi)009:29: klong dgu bam po nyi khri le'u khri drug stong yod pa las /
NK032(khi)009:31: gnyis su med pa lta ba'i klong /
NK032(khi)009:32: yengs pa med pa sgom pa'i klong /
NK032(khi)009:33: blang dor med pa spyod pa'i klong /
NK032(khi)009:34: lhun gyis grub pa 'bras bu'i klong /
NK032(khi)009:35: bgrod du med pa lam gyi klong /
NK032(khi)009:36: mtha' dbus med pa dal gyi klong /
NK032(khi)009:37: spyi blugs tshangs pa dbang gi klong /
NK032(khi)009:38: 'da' ba med pa dam tshig gi klong /
NK032(khi)009:39: rtsol ba med pa phrin las kyi klong dang dagu'o //
NK032(khi)009:40: bam po nyi khri dang le'u khri drug stong ni /
NK032(khi)009:41: smos kyi mi langs pas 'dir ma bshad do //
NK032(khi)009:43: slob dpon bee ro tsa nas /
NK032(khi)009:44: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan la bshad pa ni bka' babs dang po'o //
NK032(khi)009:45: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la bshad pa ni bka' babs par pa'o //
NK032(khi)009:46: spang mi pham mgon po la gtad pa ni bka' babs tha ma'o //
NK032(khi)009:48: yang dag don gcig mchis pa de //
NK032(khi)009:49: mi pham mgon po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)009:50: ces pa brgyud pa tha ma'i gdams ngag yin no //
NK032(khi)009:51: brgyud pa tha ma'i lugs kyi klong dgu bam po
NK032(khi)009:52: nyi khri le'u khri drug stong yod pa las phye
NK032(khi)009:53: bas rdo rje snying po'i don gtan la 'bebs pa'i
NK032(khi)009:55: pad+ma'i snying po'i don nyams su len pa'i sgrub sde bcu gsum du byung ba las /
NK032(khi)009:56: spyir brgyud pa phyi mar man ngag gi rgyud drug la /
NK032(khi)009:57: lta ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)009:58: sgom pa rgya mtsho dang mnyam pa'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)009:59: spyod pa ri bo dang mnyam pa'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)009:60: 'bras bu yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che dang mnyam pa'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)009:61: dam tshig rgyal khrims dang mnyam pa'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)009:62: phrin las rgyal po gdan la bzhugs pa lta bu'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)009:63: rgyud bu chung bcu gnyis te bco brgyad /
NK032(khi)009:65: ye shes rdzogs pa rin po che ye shes gsang ba 'od dang /
NK032(khi)009:66: rtsa ba'i rgyud sde gsum dang nyi shu rtsa gcig yod /
NK032(khi)009:67: rdo rje snying pa'i don gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud sde bcu gsum du 'dod pa ni /
NK032(khi)009:68: rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba dang gcig /
NK032(khi)009:69: bshad pa'i rgyud badz+ra bka' sa man+ta nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud gnyis /
NK032(khi)009:70: sgom pa'i rgyud ye shes rdzogs pa dang gsum /
NK032(khi)009:71: dka' ba spyod pa klong dgu'i rgyud dang bzhi /
NK032(khi)009:72: ye shes bdun kun 'byung yang snang /
NK032(khi)009:74: nya mo 'khor lo'i rgyud dang drug /
NK032(khi)009:75: spyod pa 'dus pa rgya mtsho sgrol ma'i rgyud dang bdun /
NK032(khi)009:76: e a ra li rnyog pa med pa'i rgyud dang brgyad /
NK032(khi)009:77: snying po don gyi rgyud dang dgu /
NK032(khi)009:78: rig pa nam mkha' ltar gsal ba'i rgyud dang bcu tham pa /
NK032(khi)009:79: mdo lnga snying po'i rgyud dang bcu gcig /
NK032(khi)009:80: bka' sa man+ta phyi ma'i phyi ma 'od kyi rgyud dang bcu gnyis /
NK032(khi)009:81: thag ring ba'i rgyud dang bcu gsum mo //
NK032(khi)009:82: pad+ma'i snying po'i don nyams su blang ba'i sgrub sde bcu gsum la /
NK032(khi)009:83: de dag thams cad kyi man ngag rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa dbang gi man ngag dang gcig /
NK032(khi)009:84: zam pa chen po gsum 'phrul snang /
NK032(khi)009:85: gyi me long brtsegs pa chen po dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)009:86: zam pa chung ngu dang gsum /
NK032(khi)009:90: 'gro drug g.yang sa bcad pa dang bdun /
NK032(khi)009:91: rin po che pra khrid dang brgyad /
NK032(khi)009:92: rna brgyud tshig gsum dang dgu /
NK032(khi)009:93: lan gyi dpe cha bzhi yang snang /
NK032(khi)009:95: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i man ngag dang bcu gcig /
NK032(khi)009:96: de dag thams cad kyi don bsdus pa rna brgyud lung gser yang snang /
NK032(khi)009:97: gi phreng ba dang bcu gnyis /
NK032(khi)009:98: theg pa thams cad kyi don bsdus pa rin po che gser rdzong me bzang po yang snang /
NK032(khi)009:100: bka' sa man+ta nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud
NK032(khi)009:101: 'di gser gyi glegs bam la bee d+aur+ya zhun mas
NK032(khi)009:102: rang nan du bris pa'i po ti chag gang ba
NK032(khi)009:103: gcig sems dag lha'i bus dga' rab rdo rje la
NK032(khi)009:104: gtad / des 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la gtad /
NK032(khi)009:106: sh+r+ai sid+hasa kha phyes pas sgrub sde bcu gsum dang rgyud sde bcu gsum du mdzad do //
NK032(khi)009:107: de bee ro tsa na la gtad pas rdzogs pa
NK032(khi)009:108: chen po'i brgyud pa tha ma zhes bya bar yang
NK032(khi)009:109: grags so // 'di ni de dag thams cad kyi
NK032(khi)009:110: don dang mi 'gal ba rna brgyud rin po che
NK032(khi)009:111: rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag rgyud sde bcu gsum
NK032(khi)009:112: grags so // dang / sgrub sde bcu gsum las /
NK032(khi)009:113: pha rgyud g.yo ba rlung 'dzin par byed pa gdams ngag gi brgyud pa /
NK032(khi)009:114: ma rgyud bde ba nyams 'char bar byed pa byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa dang gnyis su 'dus so //
NK032(khi)009:115: de nyid kyang nye bar bsdu na /
NK032(khi)009:116: pha rgyud kyi don bsdus pa g.yo 'dzin rlung gi man ngag /
NK032(khi)009:117: ma rgyud don bsdus pa bde ba thig le'i man ngag go //
NK032(khi)009:118: de gnyis kyi don gcig tu bsdus pas /
NK032(khi)009:119: sgra ru smrar ma btub bsam du ma btub par rgyud la gnas pa'i don de dus kyi brda /
NK032(khi)009:120: de rig cing rtogs par byed pa'i thabs gnad kyi
NK032(khi)009:121: brda' bzhis gsal ba mi rtog pa bde ba gsum
NK032(khi)009:122: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed par gnas gyur nas /
NK032(khi)009:123: gsal ba mi rtog pa bde ba gsum ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa gcig tu 'dus /
NK032(khi)009:124: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)009:125: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi mtha'
NK032(khi)009:126: zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa de
NK032(khi)009:127: la / blo'i yul du byas pa'i bsam rgyu'am /
NK032(khi)009:128: bsgom rgyu gcig kyang med pas na sgom med blo'i
NK032(khi)009:129: spyod yul du ma gyur pa de don dam pa
NK032(khi)009:131: blo bral gyi don de rkyen gyis mi 'chug mi 'gyur bas na gzer /
NK032(khi)009:132: de la re ba dang dogs pa'i blo med pas na dbyings so //
NK032(khi)009:133: don de la rdo rje zam pa'i dbu nas zhabs su ma lus pa'i don sbyar nas /
NK032(khi)009:134: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod du med pa'i don de yang /
NK032(khi)009:135: blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba
NK032(khi)009:136: tsam yang mi gnas pa'i bsgom du med pa'i don
NK032(khi)009:137: de rang yin / gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub
NK032(khi)009:138: sems nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don bstan pa
NK032(khi)009:139: de rang yin / yang / bsgom du med pa'i don de rang ston pa yin /
NK032(khi)009:140: rna brgyud lung gi gter chen 'grol ba yang /
NK032(khi)009:141: bsgom med don gyi gter rnyed pas /
NK032(khi)009:142: gzung 'dzin dang bral nas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol ba yin /
NK032(khi)009:143: bsgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa yang /
NK032(khi)009:144: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'i don dam pa /
NK032(khi)009:145: mi 'chug mi 'gyur rkyen gyis mi 'jig pa'i gzer de rang yin /
NK032(khi)009:146: re dogs med pa'i dbyings su gtad pa yang /
NK032(khi)009:147: re ba dang dogs pa'i blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi
NK032(khi)009:148: mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'i
NK032(khi)009:149: dbyings la bstan pa de rang yin no //
NK032(khi)009:150: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas
NK032(khi)009:151: pas sems nyid rnam par dag pa'i don la dbang
NK032(khi)009:152: thob pas / dbang ngang gis rdzogs pas sgom sgrub
NK032(khi)009:153: dge ba'i chos la mi ltos par sems nyid rnam
NK032(khi)009:154: par dag pa gtan la phebs pa yang de rang
NK032(khi)009:155: thob pas / yin / blo'i mtha' zab cing phra
NK032(khi)009:156: ba tsam yang mi gnas par gnyis 'dzin dang bral
NK032(khi)009:157: ba de la sku rang chas su gyur pas gnyis
NK032(khi)009:158: 'dzin las grol ba yang de rang yin /
NK032(khi)009:159: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa gcig tu rtogs pas /
NK032(khi)009:160: don la rtogs dpyod byar ma btub pas /
NK032(khi)009:161: don gcig tu rtogs pas rtog dpyod las 'das pa yang de rang yin no //
NK032(khi)009:162: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa de la /
NK032(khi)009:163: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don blo'i
NK032(khi)009:164: spyod yul du ma gyur pa de rang yin pas
NK032(khi)009:165: nas / don 'di ni yang de yin /
NK032(khi)009:166: de la 'jog pa'i dus na mnyam bzhag gi dus /
NK032(khi)009:167: ldang ba'i dus na rjes thob kyi dus yin pas na /
NK032(khi)009:168: dus 'di ni yang de rang yin no //
NK032(khi)009:169: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa de /
NK032(khi)009:170: don chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i gnas lugs la ngo sprad nas /
NK032(khi)009:171: goms 'dris lam du byas pas na /
NK032(khi)009:172: rdo rje'i lam mchog kyang de rang yin /
NK032(khi)009:173: skal ba dang ldan pas gdams ngag 'di dang 'phrad pa rnams /
NK032(khi)009:174: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'i don de rtogs pa tsam gyis /
NK032(khi)009:175: spang bya dang bsgrub bya'i 'bad rtsol med pas gnyis su 'dzin pa'i blo las grol bas /
NK032(khi)009:176: skal ldan 'bad pa med par grol ba yang de rang yin /
NK032(khi)009:177: grol ba rang grol gzhan la min pa ni /
NK032(khi)009:178: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pas /
NK032(khi)009:179: gnyis su 'dzin pa'i blo mi gnas pa rang bzhin med par grol ba las /
NK032(khi)009:180: gzhan du grol rgyu med pa'o //
NK032(khi)009:181: de yang gdams ngag 'di la brgyud pa ma nor
NK032(khi)009:182: ba bzhi'i rkya bar du bcug nas don ma nor
NK032(khi)009:183: bar tshang bar ston pa 'di yin te /
NK032(khi)009:188: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa dang bzhi'o //
NK032(khi)009:190: pha med kyi bu rus stor ba dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)009:191: gang gi chos yin cha med par 'gro ste /
NK032(khi)009:192: yid mi ches pa'i skyon yod /
NK032(khi)009:193: tshig gi brgyud pa chad na /
NK032(khi)009:194: rgyal po gdung rgyud chad pa dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)009:195: tshig gi rtsa ba mi tshang bas /
NK032(khi)009:196: don gnad du bsgril mi shes te /
NK032(khi)009:197: gnas lugs gtan la mi phebs pas /
NK032(khi)009:198: don mi rtogs pa'i skyon yod /
NK032(khi)009:200: long ba 'khar ba bral ba dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)009:201: ma nor ba'i don ngo sprod gcig gi thog tu bzhag sa med pas /
NK032(khi)009:202: don thog tu ma phebs pas gol sa ru shor
NK032(khi)009:203: nas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi thob pa'i skyon yod
NK032(khi)009:204: / byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa med na /
NK032(khi)009:205: mdzod tshang mang gi sgron me shi ba dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)009:206: byin rlabs kyi bka' chad pas mkha' 'gro ma'i ko long du gyur nas /
NK032(khi)009:207: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub mi thob pa'i skyon yod /
NK032(khi)009:208: bka'i brgyud pa ma chad na /
NK032(khi)009:209: bka' brgyud kyi dgongs pa lon /
NK032(khi)009:210: tshig gi brgyud pa ma chad na /
NK032(khi)009:212: brda'i brgyud pa ma chad na /
NK032(khi)009:214: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa ma chad na /
NK032(khi)009:215: mkha' 'gro ma'i ko long du mi 'gro ste /
NK032(khi)009:216: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub thob /
NK032(khi)009:217: 'dir ni bka'i brgyud pa ma chad de /
NK032(khi)009:218: rna brgyud lung gi gter chen dgrol ba yin /
NK032(khi)009:219: tshig gi brgyud pa ma chad de /
NK032(khi)009:220: rdo rje'i tshig lam sems kyi lde mig bstan pa yin /
NK032(khi)009:221: brda'i brgyud pa ma chad de /
NK032(khi)009:222: brda bzhis rgyud la sbyor ba bstan pa yin /
NK032(khi)009:223: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa ma chad de /
NK032(khi)009:224: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs a ha ho'i bstan pa yin no //
NK032(khi)009:225: rgya gar gyi yul na byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa
NK032(khi)009:226: la dbang gi chu bo chen po bzhi yod pa
NK032(khi)009:227: las rgyal po dzahl po ti glegs bam gyi dbang
NK032(khi)009:228: babs / slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas la lha ma srin sde brgyad kyi dbang babs /
NK032(khi)009:229: slon dpon bi ma la mi tra la pan+di ta lnga brgya'i dbang babs /
NK032(khi)009:230: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje la ye shes lha'i dbang babs pa'o //
NK032(khi)009:232: rgyal thabs spyi blugs tshangs pa'i dbang /
NK032(khi)009:233: sbyor ba dag pa'i dbang dang /
NK032(khi)009:236: gnyis ka rgyun ma chad pa ru bka' babs pa'o //
NK032(khi)009:237: bka' sa man+ta nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud
NK032(khi)009:238: kyi don bsdus pa'i rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa
NK032(khi)009:239: skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas /
NK032(khi)009:240: tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba'i man ngag gi khog chings rdzogs so //
